column2: Migrated from EPA STORET Legacy Database- originally reported by Wisconsin DNR
Sunny- slight. chop- lake turning over- green in protected areas
Sunny- 4-6" chop- surface dirt- needles- leaves- etc.  Lake level: very high
Sunny- 4-6" waves- water discolored (tamarack).  Lake level: very high
mostly sunny---7geese spotted---1 water skier----2 boats passing through mostly sunny---rained overnight .5 inches---7geese spotted---1 water skier----2 boats passing through

Partly cloudy. Lakefront homeowners asked what they thought of the condition of the lake compared to past years-"water seemed clearer and less silty-less brown 'fuzz' on the kids when they get out"- "really cold about 8" off the surface"- "awesome". Kayaked out to deepest part of the lake-dragonflies- muskrat kept me company.
Not as much 'matter' in the water.
partly sunny-8mph wind-1 boat passing through-no wildlife spotted
sunny with light wind----1 boat passing through-----a gaggle of geese ( 5 ) spotted----pine tree pollen visible in the water column
partly sunny light wind ----- no boats ---- no wildlife spotted
sunny with light wind------1 boat passing through----no wild life spotted
sunny with a light wind----particles suspended in the water column---no boats--no wildlife
sunny calm wind----no wildlife spotted---1 boat passing through----no wildlife spotted---green on lake surface
sunny with a light wind---no wildlife spotted---no boats---looking through the water column is like looking through a muddy snow globe
partly cloudy....light wind....2 boats fishing 1 boat passing through...Had wife recording data
overcast with a light breeze----no boats or wildlife spotted
sunny with a light breeze---3 jet ski-----1water ski-----no wildlife spotted
sunny with a light breeze-----2-boats passing through--no wildlife spotted
sunny with calm wind----green in the water column----2 kayaks---no wildlife spotted
mostly overcast...light wind.....1 boat fishing...1 boat passing through....no wildlife spotted
sunny with a light wind----no boats----2 loons spotted----last check of the season!!!!!!
MOSTLY SUNNY----1 BOAT FISHING----1 PONTOON BOAT---NO WILDLIFE SPOTTED
sunny with a light wind-----no wild life spotted
sunny with a light breeze---2 kayak---1 personal water craft--
sunny with a light north wind---1 boat fishing----no wildlife spotted
sunny with a west wind---7 geese---1 boat
partly sunny  light breeze----0 boats----no wildlife spotted
partly sunny north wind.....no boats or wildlife spotted
sunny @ windy  11 geese no boats spotted
Sunny with a light wind---no wildlife spotted---2 boats fishing 1 waterskiing-----the wife recorded the data
mostly sunny south wind----water dark in color---no boats or wildlife-----my CFO aka the wife recorded the data
mostly sunny with a light wind----1 boat fishing---no wildlife spotted----wife recorded the data
mostly sunny--light breeze--algae in the water column and on the surface--no wildlife spotted--2 boats passing through--wife recorded data
